  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Guest Services Agent",
  "description": "<p><strong>Main Responsibilities</strong></p><p>· To provide a courteous and professional service at all times.</p><p>· Welcome guests in a friendly, prompt and professional manner.</p><p>· To process check-in/check-out including luggage assistance and collect payments in compliance with cash handling, credit card processing and accounting policies and procedures</p><p>· To provide information about hotel services and amenities</p><p>· To ensure all guests’ information are strictly confidential for use by authorized personnel only</p><p>· Attend to guest request and complaints and provide guest with feedback, when necessary to ensure guests’ satisfaction</p><p>· To have a complete understanding of and adhere to the hotel's policy relating to fire, hygiene, health and safety.</p><p>· To maintain good working relationships with your own colleagues, and all other departments.</p><p>.</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>· Secondary education</p><p>· A positive and keen to learn attitude</p><p>· Passion to deliver exceptional levels of guest services</p><p>· Able to multi-task and detail oriented</p><p>· Good interpersonal and communications skills</p><p>· Able to work shift, weekends and public holidays</p><p>· Competent in MS Office applications.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified. **</p>",
