    "description": "<p>Located in the heart of Bugis’ shopping, arts and cultural districts, Mercure Singapore Bugis is an international branded hotel situated next to the Bugis+ shopping centre and within a 5-minute walk to Bugis MRT station.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The hotel features 395 funky heritage inspired rooms, as well as two restaurants including a Western and a Chinese restaurant, 6 meeting rooms, a lobby bar, a swimming pool, fitness lounge, jacuzzi and many outdoor spaces for events including a Skydeck on the top floor of the hotel.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The hotel’s proximity to the city’s main landmark attractions, and accessibility via public transportation ensure this is a high profile hotel in the middle of Singapore.</p>",
